Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.18,0:00:20.35,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] Here it is.\NMy favorite place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.52,0:00:24.77,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] No one ever\Ncomes around to this side.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.86,0:00:27.32,Main,,0,0,0,,So it's always nice and quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.40,0:00:28.53,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.61,0:00:30.61,Main,,0,0,0,,So this is where you\Nhave your card battles?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.70,0:00:31.70,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.78,0:00:34.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. I only got\Nmy cards recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:37.37,Main,,0,0,0,,I just like quiet places.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.45,0:00:39.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Actually, the\Nmatch with Akira...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.62,0:00:43.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Um... It was my...\Nfirst battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.08,0:00:45.30,Main,,0,0,0,,I do come here to\Npractice a bit, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.38,0:00:47.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Midoriko cooks up\Ndifferent battle situations
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.92,0:00:51.22,Main,,0,0,0,,and gives me tips\Non how to handle them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.30,0:00:52.97,Main,,0,0,0,,I take notes, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.30,0:00:55.97,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Wow. Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.06,0:00:59.39,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] N-no, don't\Nlook! I-it's a secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.48,0:01:02.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Besides, they're\Npretty much useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.35,0:01:05.27,Main,,0,0,0,,You saw how much good they\Ndid in my battle, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.36,0:01:06.94,Main,,0,0,0,,I just wasn't ready yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.03,0:01:08.94,Main,,0,0,0,,I feel so... I dunno... lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.03,0:01:10.49,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Huh? I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.57,0:01:12.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Why do you want\Nto battle me then?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.74,0:01:14.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.53,0:01:18.37,Main,,0,0,0,,You didn't seem very strong,\Nso I thought I would be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.45,0:01:21.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Dang. Not pulling\Nany punches huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.12,0:01:22.29,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.37,0:01:25.42,Main,,0,0,0,,I... know it's wrong!\NBut, no matter what...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.50,0:01:28.55,Main,,0,0,0,,I just... I have to win this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.63,0:01:31.22,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Her wish must\Nreally mean a lot to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.30,0:01:34.34,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.43,0:01:38.60,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] If I lost, at least I\Nwould be helping someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.68,0:01:42.02,Main,,0,0,0,,And maybe it would give\Nher some confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.10,0:01:43.39,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.48,0:01:44.90,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.98,0:01:50.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.36,0:01:53.49,Main,,0,0,0,,All right. Let's have a battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.57,0:01:55.66,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.49,0:01:58.91,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.30,0:03:45.10,Main,,0,0,0,,OMG. Can I call you "Yuzu-poo?".\NI'm gonna call you Yuzu-poo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.18,0:03:45.81,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.89,0:03:47.31,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.02,0:03:52.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh! I go first!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.65,0:03:58.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Draw, Ener Charge!\NSummon, Amethyst!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.20,0:04:04.33,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] If she uses that stupid\Npeeping thing, I'm screwed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.41,0:04:07.29,Main,,0,0,0,,With the power of Amethyst,\NI'll banish the Refries.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.37,0:04:09.08,Main,,0,0,0,,And attack Sapphire!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.16,0:04:10.63,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] I'll go all out\Nand crush her before she
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.71,0:04:12.38,Main,,0,0,0,,levels enough\Nto use that move!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.46,0:04:13.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Hanayo, Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.79,0:04:15.21,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.05,0:04:20.84,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] Ouch! So aggressive!\NYou're a real bully, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.93,0:04:22.18,Main,,0,0,0,,See how you like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.26,0:04:23.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Piriluk. Grow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.60,0:04:29.06,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] Here's a spell\Nfor you! Bye-bye Mr. Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.14,0:04:31.40,Main,,0,0,0,,What a pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.48,0:04:32.31,Main,,0,0,0,,It's all good...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.40,0:04:33.98,Main,,0,0,0,,What shall I choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.06,0:04:36.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's see... That one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.87,0:04:44.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Aw. Only Level 1? Lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.45,0:04:45.87,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.95,0:04:47.08,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] You can't just smother\Nyour opponent with a bunch
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.16,0:04:48.45,Main,,0,0,0,,of weaksauce cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.54,0:04:50.04,Main,,0,0,0,,You're gonna eat those words\Nwhen I clean the floor
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.12,0:04:51.29,Main,,0,0,0,,with your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.37,0:04:53.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Just trying to give you\Nsome friendly advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.63,0:04:55.96,Main,,0,0,0,,I know red decks are supposed\Nto be, like, straightforward
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.05,0:04:57.55,Main,,0,0,0,,and all, but jeez, loosen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.63,0:04:58.88,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.96,0:05:02.26,Main,,0,0,0,,[KAZUKI] Your gameplay is\Nway too straightforward.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.34,0:05:04.80,Main,,0,0,0,,And what's so wrong\Nwith being straightforward?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.89,0:05:06.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.28,0:05:21.03,Main,,0,0,0,,The field here seems\Ntotally different
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.11,0:05:22.91,Main,,0,0,0,,than my battle against Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.99,0:05:25.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Sounds weird, but it\Nalmost feels warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.70,0:05:26.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.08,0:05:30.12,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not anything like\NYuzuki's field, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.20,0:05:32.62,Main,,0,0,0,,We've even got a\Nnice breeze, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.71,0:05:35.29,Main,,0,0,0,,[MIDORIKO] Our setting is a\Nmanifestation of the affinity
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.38,0:05:36.75,Main,,0,0,0,,between the Selectors.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.84,0:05:37.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Affinity?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.96,0:05:40.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Your deck is green\Nand Ruko's is white.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.01,0:05:43.26,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a bit of a\Nrare combination.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.34,0:05:46.72,Main,,0,0,0,,But when the two come together,\Na warm light is born.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.81,0:05:48.22,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.31,0:05:51.27,Main,,0,0,0,,I feel like I can just relax\Nand enjoy myself this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.35,0:05:52.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.19,0:05:53.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Good! Let's do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.02,0:05:58.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe's LRIG is nice\Ntoo. I hope they win.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.15,0:05:59.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Meow?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.49,0:06:05.07,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] You're first,\NRuko! Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.16,0:06:07.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.32,0:06:09.91,Main,,0,0,0,,First I draw... Ener Charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.99,0:06:12.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama, Grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.96,0:06:14.62,Main,,0,0,0,,No Level 1 cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.71,0:06:15.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Your turn now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.75,0:06:16.79,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.88,0:06:18.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Drawing 2 cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.21,0:06:19.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Ener Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.42,0:06:21.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Summon: Mi-Ke and Mi-Ke!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.30,0:06:27.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Mi-Ke! Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.30,0:06:28.72,Main,,0,0,0,,[MIDORIKO grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.26,0:06:32.23,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.31,0:06:33.69,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA shouts]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.77,0:06:35.89,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] This is intense.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.98,0:06:38.81,Main,,0,0,0,,It's nothing like playing with\NGrandma, that's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.90,0:06:40.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Hah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.44,0:06:42.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] My ears are burning...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.28,0:06:45.57,Main,,0,0,0,,When the attacks hit,\Nit's almost painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.65,0:06:50.49,Main,,0,0,0,,But I'm happy. And...\NI wanna keep on fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.58,0:06:54.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama, Grow to level 2!\NRound and Square!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.46,0:06:57.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Attack Mi-Ke with\NRound and Banish!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.38,0:06:58.46,Main,,0,0,0,,[MIDORIKO grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.54,0:07:00.09,Main,,0,0,0,,And now attack\Nwith Square!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.17,0:07:01.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Midoriko! Block it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.71,0:07:03.42,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA squeals]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.51,0:07:05.72,Main,,0,0,0,,[MIDORIKO grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.80,0:07:07.01,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Tama, attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.09,0:07:09.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Wha--! Again?! Get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.35,0:07:10.56,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.51,0:07:16.52,Main,,0,0,0,,[MIDORIKO grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.61,0:07:20.11,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA cheers]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.19,0:07:21.52,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.61,0:07:24.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about me!\NJust use Grow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.15,0:07:25.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.15,0:07:28.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Midoriko: Level 2!\NSummon: Shiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.03,0:07:30.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Midoriko Arts: Giant!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.82,0:07:34.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Shiro's power gains plus five\Nthousand in the next turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.16,0:07:35.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Shiro, attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.12,0:07:40.92,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.30,0:07:47.68,Main,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't win. It's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.72,0:07:50.18,Main,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.26,0:07:52.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, whatever it is,\Nit's not our problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.89,0:07:54.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Time to attack! And quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.81,0:07:56.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah... Okay, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.06,0:07:58.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Because... I don't--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.02,0:08:01.61,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.69,0:08:03.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.53,0:08:06.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, Piriluk. Grow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.49,0:08:11.20,Main,,0,0,0,,My Ener's\Nnot ready yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.28,0:08:16.25,Main,,0,0,0,,[PIRILUK] Arts. Peeping Analyze.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.33,0:08:18.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Be strong, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.29,0:08:19.46,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.54,0:08:20.88,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] I knew it was coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.96,0:08:24.09,Main,,0,0,0,,That move doesn't just attack\Nmy cards. It attacks me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.17,0:08:26.92,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] Let's find out your\Nlittle wish, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.01,0:08:29.26,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] She'll know.\NShe'll know my secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.34,0:08:32.10,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO] Who cares\Nif she finds out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.18,0:08:33.64,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Hanayo...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.72,0:08:35.22,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO] If your wish comes\Ntrue, everyone will know anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.31,0:08:38.31,Main,,0,0,0,,won't they? Just\Nbrace yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.39,0:08:40.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Knowing her, she'll probably\Nsay something horrible
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.60,0:08:41.81,Main,,0,0,0,,to get under your skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.90,0:08:44.36,Main,,0,0,0,,But remember:\Nyour wish is nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.44,0:08:45.98,Main,,0,0,0,,for you to be ashamed of!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.86,0:08:51.74,Main,,0,0,0,,First, toss out all those\Nlevel one cards of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.82,0:08:52.99,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.07,0:08:55.74,Main,,0,0,0,,And then the fun part!\NShow me your big wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.83,0:08:57.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Piriluk, go peek-a-boo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.46,0:09:05.63,Main,,0,0,0,,That's immoral.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.71,0:09:07.55,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.63,0:09:09.80,Main,,0,0,0,,She's in love\Nwith her twin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.43,0:09:12.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoa! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.93,0:09:15.43,Main,,0,0,0,,You're sayin' that shrimpy\Ndude you were makin' doe eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.51,0:09:16.97,Main,,0,0,0,,at before is\Nyour twin brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.06,0:09:19.18,Main,,0,0,0,,--Stay calm.\N--Yeah, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.27,0:09:20.23,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.31,0:09:22.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Gawd, that is\Nsuper-duper naughty!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.31,0:09:25.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, maybe it's a little hot.\NBut not, like, for real!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.90,0:09:28.82,Main,,0,0,0,,--You dirty girl!\N--Please, shut up. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.90,0:09:31.70,Main,,0,0,0,,You know, they have a\Nword for that sort of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.78,0:09:35.28,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't say it.\NBut it's spelled:
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.37,0:09:37.33,Main,,0,0,0,,I-N-C.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.41,0:09:39.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Shut your whore mouth!\NThat's enough, ya hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.87,0:09:42.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.21,0:09:44.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.38,0:09:46.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Use Dominating Fury!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.34,0:09:48.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you out of your mind?!\NYou can't use such a
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.42,0:09:50.26,Main,,0,0,0,,high energy\NArt right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.34,0:09:53.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop it! This instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.64,0:09:57.64,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.72,0:10:00.68,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] If I win, Hitoe's\Nwish won't come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.77,0:10:02.89,Main,,0,0,0,,And I don't even have\Nanything to fight for.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.98,0:10:04.19,Main,,0,0,0,,But still!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.27,0:10:04.85,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.94,0:10:05.86,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.94,0:10:08.44,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] Tama. Want to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.52,0:10:12.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Hold on. Did you just\Nspeak a whole sentence?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.86,0:10:16.78,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] Tama. Wants to\Nwin. The battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.87,0:10:19.87,Main,,0,0,0,,No giving up!\NI don't want to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.95,0:10:21.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.62,0:10:25.17,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] Ruko! You weren't\Nplanning to give up were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.25,0:10:29.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Why? If you let me win the\Nbattle, there would be no point!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.09,0:10:30.84,Main,,0,0,0,,That wouldn't make me happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.92,0:10:32.34,Main,,0,0,0,,No, I just--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.42,0:10:36.30,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know why I even\Nbothered trying to hide it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.39,0:10:39.72,Main,,0,0,0,,It's obvious I don't\Nhave any friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.81,0:10:43.06,Main,,0,0,0,,I moved to Tokyo from\NAomori quite a while back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.14,0:10:45.98,Main,,0,0,0,,But I was behind in school,\Nand my accent was funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.06,0:10:49.61,Main,,0,0,0,,So everyone did their\Nbest to ignore me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.69,0:10:52.19,Main,,0,0,0,,I was completely\Nmiserable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.28,0:10:55.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Then one day, I got a letter\Nfrom a friend back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.57,0:10:59.62,Main,,0,0,0,,I read it over and\Nover again. It saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.25,0:11:03.79,Main,,0,0,0,,You have to understand:
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.87,0:11:07.00,Main,,0,0,0,,To someone like me, a friend\Nis a very precious thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.08,0:11:08.21,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.29,0:11:09.54,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] No matter how\Nbadly I want to win,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.63,0:11:12.30,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to tarnish\Nmy wish by cheating!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.38,0:11:14.17,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll give this\Neverything I've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.26,0:11:17.89,Main,,0,0,0,,And then... my wish\Nwill come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.97,0:11:20.68,Main,,0,0,0,,That was so cool. I'm jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.76,0:11:22.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.77,0:11:27.02,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] I'm sorry.\NI don't have a wish yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.10,0:11:29.69,Main,,0,0,0,,But I still wanna battle\Nwith all I've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.48,0:11:32.73,Main,,0,0,0,,--[TAMA squeals delightedly]\N--Let's give it our best!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.82,0:11:33.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Win or lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.82,0:11:34.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.74,0:11:35.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Ruko!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.82,0:11:37.86,Main,,0,0,0,,All right! Let's\Nshow 'em what we got!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.95,0:11:39.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.91,0:11:42.99,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] This is fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.08,0:11:44.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama, attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.12,0:11:45.75,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA shouts]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.83,0:11:47.79,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] It doesn't matter\Nwhat happens anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.87,0:11:50.38,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm so excited,\NI could almost scream!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.46,0:11:53.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Oversize! Power-up\Nall of the SIGNIs!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.38,0:11:56.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah? I don't think\Nso! Anti-Spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.76,0:11:58.01,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA squeals]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.09,0:12:01.01,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] I've never felt\Nanything like this before!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.10,0:12:02.30,Main,,0,0,0,,[MIDORIKO grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.39,0:12:03.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Midoriko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.89,0:12:06.85,Main,,0,0,0,,[MIDORIKO] I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.93,0:12:08.52,Main,,0,0,0,,[MIDORIKO grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.60,0:12:11.40,Main,,0,0,0,,And, hey. Ya done good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.02,0:12:14.57,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.65,0:12:21.12,Main,,0,0,0,,It's over? Guess I won.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.20,0:12:23.83,Main,,0,0,0,,So, this is\Na real battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.91,0:12:26.91,Main,,0,0,0,,I had... no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.83,0:12:32.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait a second.\NI thought it was over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.04,0:12:36.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Why aren't we going\Nback to the real world?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.42,0:12:40.59,Main,,0,0,0,,What should we do? Hey, Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.68,0:12:41.55,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.64,0:12:42.89,Main,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.97,0:12:48.48,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.56,0:12:49.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.40,0:12:59.15,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.24,0:12:59.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.03,0:13:01.53,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.79,0:13:09.21,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.29,0:13:11.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Looks like\Nshe evolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.12,0:13:14.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Evolved? Is that different\Nfrom powering up with "Grow?"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.84,0:13:17.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah. As Selectors\Ndraw closer and closer
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.38,0:13:20.67,Main,,0,0,0,,to becoming an Eternal Girl,\Ntheir LRIGs take on new forms
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.76,0:13:23.39,Main,,0,0,0,,and develop greater powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.47,0:13:26.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow! You're amazing, Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.39,0:13:28.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Aww, thanks, Ru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.27,0:13:31.19,Main,,0,0,0,,And... you're still talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.32,0:13:37.57,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.65,0:13:39.07,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE groans softly]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.87,0:13:44.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.78,0:13:46.08,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.16,0:13:48.45,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess she keeps her\Nevolved form even after
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.54,0:13:50.37,Main,,0,0,0,,the battle's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.46,0:13:55.00,Main,,0,0,0,,You're right. The text printed\Non the card changed, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.09,0:13:57.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Um... I'm sorry. I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.21,0:14:00.34,Main,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have said\Nwhat I said before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.42,0:14:03.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Obviously, you two are\Nmore than strong enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.09,0:14:05.01,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] That's sweet of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.10,0:14:06.85,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] One more loss\Nand I'm finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.93,0:14:08.97,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't say things have\Ngone quite like I planned,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.06,0:14:11.39,Main,,0,0,0,,but this was my choice.\NSo no matter what happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.48,0:14:13.02,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't have any regrets!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.10,0:14:14.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Except for not getting\Nmy wish, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.06,0:14:16.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Um... Hitoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.86,0:14:18.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.19,0:14:20.40,Main,,0,0,0,,So I was thinking, outside\Nof all this Eternal Girl
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.49,0:14:23.49,Main,,0,0,0,,battle stuff, you and I\Ncould maybe just be friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.57,0:14:25.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Wha--?! Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.41,0:14:28.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Of course! I actually\Njust moved here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.28,0:14:30.33,Main,,0,0,0,,So I haven't made\Nmany friends, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.41,0:14:32.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Bu-- You...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.29,0:14:35.92,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't care at first. But\Nnow that I've opened up more.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.00,0:14:37.59,Main,,0,0,0,,I... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.67,0:14:39.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, this is getting,\Nlike, super awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.80,0:14:40.71,Main,,0,0,0,,If you don't want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.80,0:14:42.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh no, that would\Nbe wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.51,0:14:43.22,Main,,0,0,0,,[WOMAN] Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.30,0:14:44.55,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOTH gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.63,0:14:46.80,Main,,0,0,0,,This is a library. Can you\Nkeep it down, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.89,0:14:48.93,Main,,0,0,0,,--Right! Sorry...\N--Right! So sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.01,0:14:50.72,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] So, um... I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.81,0:14:54.73,Main,,0,0,0,,I think I need some\Ntime to process this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.81,0:14:56.23,Main,,0,0,0,,All right, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.40,0:15:00.69,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA snores softly]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.77,0:15:02.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Already zonked!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.99,0:15:04.40,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.07,0:15:10.16,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Ugh. It's getting late!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.24,0:15:12.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Wish I had a cell phone,\Nso I could call home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.50,0:15:17.92,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.42,0:15:21.50,Main,,0,0,0,,[HATSU] Oh, neat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.59,0:15:23.84,Main,,0,0,0,,You bought a book\Nabout your card game?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.92,0:15:25.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Looks quite\Ncomprehensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.97,0:15:28.47,Main,,0,0,0,,After you study up\Non this, I bet no one
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.55,0:15:29.93,Main,,0,0,0,,will be able to beat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.01,0:15:32.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah. There's a lotta\Ncards here I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.14,0:15:34.23,Main,,0,0,0,,This one looks\Npretty awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.23,0:15:37.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you have a\Nsecret strategy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.06,0:15:40.90,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] I wish. But\Nmaybe with a little work!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.98,0:15:43.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I got the idea\Nfrom a girl I met today
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.28,0:15:45.11,Main,,0,0,0,,who took all kinds of\Nnotes on the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.20,0:15:46.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Does that mean you\Nmade another friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.82,0:15:48.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah. At least I hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.37,0:15:52.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.83,0:15:54.50,Main,,0,0,0,,[kettle whistles]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.58,0:15:56.25,Main,,0,0,0,,All right, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.33,0:15:58.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Once I'm done making dinner,\Nlet Grandma have a look
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.46,0:15:59.96,Main,,0,0,0,,at that book of yours, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.04,0:16:02.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, and then\Nwe'll have a battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.21,0:16:06.59,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Let's see...\NWith Tama's new powers,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.67,0:16:08.18,Main,,0,0,0,,it looks like I can\Nuse more red cards
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.26,0:16:10.39,Main,,0,0,0,,and then activate\Nthe Search effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.47,0:16:11.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Ooh, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.80,0:16:13.64,Main,,0,0,0,,I'd have to trade out\Nsome powerful cards
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.72,0:16:15.14,Main,,0,0,0,,if I wanted to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.23,0:16:18.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Then Yuzuki's pure red deck\Nwould have an edge for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.48,0:16:20.44,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll battle\Nbecause it's fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.52,0:16:22.36,Main,,0,0,0,,That's more than\Nenough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.44,0:16:25.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Everything else,\NI can worry about later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.15,0:16:27.11,Main,,0,0,0,,[phone ringing]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.20,0:16:30.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh. I got it Gram'ma!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.32,0:16:34.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Hello? Oh. Kazuki!\NIs something up?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.04,0:16:39.83,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] She didn't\Nsay anything to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.96,0:16:44.96,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.05,0:16:47.09,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] So Yuzuki still\Nhasn't come home yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.17,0:16:48.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Did she call?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.09,0:16:50.68,Main,,0,0,0,,I called her,\Nbut no answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.76,0:16:54.72,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought for sure she\Nwould've been at your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.81,0:16:56.22,Main,,0,0,0,,You don't think...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.43,0:16:58.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Akira...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.43,0:16:59.44,Main,,0,0,0,,[KAZUKI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.52,0:17:03.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[train clattering]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.90,0:17:09.78,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] Aww, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.29,0:17:18.41,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] Things were\Njust getting fun
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.50,0:17:19.91,Main,,0,0,0,,and you're burnt out already?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.00,0:17:21.92,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.00,0:17:23.38,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] Don't get all butt-hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.46,0:17:24.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Really, it's no biggie!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.96,0:17:27.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Since I'm such a good pal,\NI'll put you out of your misery!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.63,0:17:32.30,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] If I had that\NAdamasphere card
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.38,0:17:36.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Kazuki was talking about,\NI could have countered this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.43,0:17:38.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, Piriluk,\Nkindly do the honors!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.89,0:17:40.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Boom!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.36,0:17:45.44,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.52,0:17:47.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Hanayoooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.90,0:17:53.03,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI sobbing softly]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.11,0:17:56.83,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] I'm sorry...\NThis is all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.91,0:17:57.49,Main,,0,0,0,,[KAZUKI] Yuzuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.58,0:17:58.99,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.87,0:18:01.75,Main,,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.83,0:18:03.54,Main,,0,0,0,,You battled Akira,\Ndidn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.88,0:18:09.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.09,0:18:11.22,Main,,0,0,0,,The least you could do\Nis explain yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.30,0:18:12.63,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.72,0:18:14.76,Main,,0,0,0,,I told you you wouldn't\Nstand a chance with your deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.84,0:18:15.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Why'd you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.76,0:18:16.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.64,0:18:17.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.85,0:18:20.06,Main,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't understand\Neven if I told you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.14,0:18:23.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't act like you care!\NLeave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.19,0:18:29.61,Main,,0,0,0,,[KAZUKI] Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.69,0:18:30.78,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.86,0:18:32.57,Main,,0,0,0,,This... This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.53,0:18:34.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Momoka tracked\None down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.95,0:18:37.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Guess I was too late. Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.49,0:18:39.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh. I get it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.16,0:18:41.54,Main,,0,0,0,,So that's what you two\Nwere talking about earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.62,0:18:43.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait, you guys\Nwere there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.17,0:18:47.17,Main,,0,0,0,,[KAZUKI] Anyway, she\Nfound another customer
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.25,0:18:50.42,Main,,0,0,0,,who was willing to trade. So she\Nworked something out for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.92,0:18:55.93,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] I feel so stupid.\NWhy didn't you tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.01,0:18:57.43,Main,,0,0,0,,you were doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.51,0:18:59.89,Main,,0,0,0,,There was a chance the\Ntrade wouldn't work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.97,0:19:03.27,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to get\Nyour hopes up for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.35,0:19:05.94,Main,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have been\Nso hard on you about losing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.02,0:19:09.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Right? I mean, you\Njust started after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.40,0:19:10.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Kazuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.28,0:19:11.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Now that you\Nhave a new card.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.69,0:19:14.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe you'll win the\Nnext match! No big whoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.07,0:19:19.20,Main,,0,0,0,,We can do this together.\NI've got your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.28,0:19:23.25,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI whimpers softly]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.33,0:19:24.66,Main,,0,0,0,,What's, uh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.75,0:19:29.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Whatever, I'm fine! I just\Nneed a moment alone, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.29,0:19:30.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.13,0:19:32.21,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Hang on.\NYuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.30,0:19:35.67,Main,,0,0,0,,It's okay. She's upset now,\Nbut she has a nice brother
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.76,0:19:37.26,Main,,0,0,0,,like you to\Nlook after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.34,0:19:39.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.39,0:19:43.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Back when I was a kid, I used\Nto be kinda shy and wimpy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.22,0:19:45.73,Main,,0,0,0,,But Yuzuki always had\Nconfidence in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.81,0:19:48.44,Main,,0,0,0,,So now, I want to do\Neverything I can for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.52,0:19:51.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Work as hard as she does\Nto make her wish come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.94,0:19:54.99,Main,,0,0,0,,I already have\Neverything I need.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.07,0:19:57.53,Main,,0,0,0,,So the least I can do is help\Nfight back some of this sadness
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.61,0:19:59.03,Main,,0,0,0,,that's eating at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.62,0:20:07.37,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Stupid Kazuki. Why is\Nhe so nice to me all the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.46,0:20:10.17,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI sobs]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.25,0:20:12.59,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Don't you realize\Nyou're just making
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.67,0:20:15.67,Main,,0,0,0,,this harder on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.01,0:20:19.18,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] Good evening, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.26,0:20:21.64,Main,,0,0,0,,[STAFF WOMAN] Akira, you're\Nlate! Hurry and get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.72,0:20:22.89,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.97,0:20:24.43,Main,,0,0,0,,[CAMERAMAN A]\NLooking good, Iona!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.52,0:20:26.60,Main,,0,0,0,,[CAMERAMAN B]\NOh, yeah-yeah, just like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.44,0:20:31.69,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] Everyone decent, I hope?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.94,0:20:39.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Damn it!\NThis is bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.24,0:20:41.78,Main,,0,0,0,,I've beaten Hitoe!\NI've beaten Yuzuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.87,0:20:44.99,Main,,0,0,0,,So why the hell isn't\Nanything changing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.08,0:20:47.50,Main,,0,0,0,,You told me I'll get kicked\Nto the curb after losing
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.58,0:20:49.83,Main,,0,0,0,,three measly battles. But\Nhow many of the damn things
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.92,0:20:52.09,Main,,0,0,0,,do I have to win to\Nbe an Eternal Girl?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.17,0:20:55.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Winning alone isn't enough to\Nqualify you as an Eternal Girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.76,0:20:58.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Certain conditions need to\Nbe met before your wish
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.13,0:20:59.09,Main,,0,0,0,,can be granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.17,0:21:01.64,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA] Like what?\NLet's hear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.72,0:21:05.22,Main,,0,0,0,,If you don't talk,\NI'll rip you in half!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.02,0:21:10.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Go on. You better hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.02,0:21:14.65,Main,,0,0,0,,If you think I'm bluffing,\Nyou're dead wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.73,0:21:16.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Tear me up, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.03,0:21:19.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Do not test me!\NYou really wanna die?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.95,0:21:21.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Get over yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.95,0:21:25.79,Main,,0,0,0,,You arrogant little shit! You're\Njust like her, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.87,0:21:29.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona. I am gonna pull\Nyour head outta your ass
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.16,0:21:31.21,Main,,0,0,0,,and drag it through\Nthe frikkin' mud.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.29,0:21:33.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Just you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.26,0:21:41.13,Main,,0,0,0,,[VOICE] Say, Iona. I just\Ngot a sense of Akira's battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.22,0:21:43.14,Main,,0,0,0,,It smells like a victory to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.22,0:21:46.89,Main,,0,0,0,,She seemed upset. Are\Nyou sure she didn't lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.97,0:21:48.31,Main,,0,0,0,,What does it\Nmatter anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.39,0:21:51.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's just crush her already!\NI wanna see her cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.73,0:21:55.52,Main,,0,0,0,,The only way she'll learn is if\Nyou grind her under your heel!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.61,0:21:58.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't make me burn you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.11,0:21:58.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Behave.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.86,0:22:01.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh. Scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.15,0:22:07.58,Main,,0,0,0,,[giggling]
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.59,0:23:41.09,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] It's nothing\Nto apologize for.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.17,0:23:42.80,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Orichalcum, attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.88,0:23:45.13,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] I wonder what it\Nfeels like to be in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.22,0:23:46.34,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.43,0:23:48.43,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] That almost\Nsounded painful for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.51,0:23:49.97,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] WIXOSS is so surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.06,0:23:53.10,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Next time:\NThat Wish Is Blasphemy.
